name: CUSTOM LABELS (6 PCS)
description:
LABEL MATES - CONTROL VINYL RECORD LABELS

CUSTOM ORDERS COME AS A SET OF (6 LABELS)

Custom Label Mates come as a (6pc) set of Control Vinyl Stickers, which cover the center label on the record. They are printed with smear proof solvent inks on long durable 4mil vinyl.

All LABEL MATES include (24) circular [45 markers] for beat juggling.

Order your custom set to match your mixmats design.

LABEL MATES are easy to apply and will last for years.

Product usually ships within 3-5 business days.
